plugins they will be none the wiser and you will have access to plugins like wreckingballrevived which is immensely useful for deleting bases rogue barricades crap lying around etc i would say the definition of vanilla is without modifications that change the game in any way rocket plugins that add kits obviously change the game but if you do not allow players to use said kits i would say the server is still vanilla simply because the players are limited to playing vanilla if admins are spawning items in or giving themselves kits i would say that the server is no longer vanilla because items that would not have existed now are existing rocket also has the ability to grant a player admin commands without showing their admin tag this serves a variety of purposes if you want to simply play the game and never have anyone know that an admin is on this is the route to go if you are forced to moderate you can simply use the commands without having a blue name displayed and nobody will ever know i find that people misbehave much more often when they do not know admins are on then when they do know they are on back before battleye as soon as i showed that i was in the server multiple
